{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "ec941d9d-b095-40bd-a06c-3e69d72d3596",
    "name": "Tech Challenge Fase 03",
    "description": "## Tech Challenge Fase 03  \n_Repo:_ [<i>https://github.com/eps364/tech-challenge-fase-03</i>](https://github.com/eps364/tech-challenge-fase-03)\n\nThis collection covers the API endpoints for the **Tech Challenge Fase 03** project, a food-ordering platform built on a **microservices architecture**. It provides a complete set of requests to interact with all services, from user authentication to order orchestration.\n\n---\n\n### Services Covered\n\n| Service | Description |\n| --- | --- |\n| **Auth Service** | User registration, login, and JWT token refresh |\n| **Client Service** | Client profile management (create, read, update, delete) |\n| **Order Service** | Order creation and listing for authenticated clients |\n| **Payment Service** | Payment creation and status retrieval |\n| **Catalog Service** | Product listing, creation, update, and deletion |\n| **Restaurant Service** | Restaurant management for owners and public browsing |\n| **Orchestration Service** | Coordinates order creation across services; includes public and private health-check endpoints |\n| **Procpag** | External payment processor integration for submitting and querying payment requests |\n\n---\n\n### Role Legend\n\nRequest names use emoji icons to indicate the required access level:\n\n- 🌐 **Public** — No authentication required\n    \n- 🙋 **Client** — Requires a valid client JWT token\n    \n- 👑 **Owner** — Requires restaurant owner privileges\n    \n- 🛠️ **Admin** — Requires administrative privileges\n    \n\n---\n\n### Getting Started\n\n1. Set the `base_url` and `procpag_url` collection variables to point to your environment.\n    \n2. Use **Auth Service - Register** or **Auth Service - Login** to obtain a JWT token.\n    \n3. The token is stored in the `jwt_token` collection variable and should be used as a Bearer token in authenticated requests.\n    \n4. Use the `refresh_token` variable with **Auth Service - Refresh Token** to renew your session.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "2416633"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🔐 🌐 Auth Service - Register",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('Status code is 201', function () {",
              "    pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
              "});",
              "",
              "var data = pm.response.json();",
              "",
              "pm.test('Response has id', function () {",
              "    pm.expect(data).to.have.property('id');",
              "});",
              "",
              "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
              "    var requestBody = JSON.parse(pm.request.body.raw);",
              "    pm.collectionVariables.set('username', requestBody.username);",
              "    pm.collectionVariables.set('password', requestBody.password);",
              "}"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "packages": {},
            "requests": {}
          }
        }
      ],
